              The dept of Pulmonary medicine at ESIC medical college and hospital was started in February 2016.Since the day of inception it has gradually expanded its services 24X7  OPD and IPD  services. The average daily OPD is 70 to 90 per day,We have 10 bedded ward ,for male and female patients and our bed occupancy throughout the year is 170% with an average IPD of 15 to 25 patients, We have five bedded RICU which has always 100% bed occupancy. 
